Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.71,Para光,,0,0,0,,Can you do that as a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:05.31,Para光,,0,0,0,,It's probably on top of the teacher's desk
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.39,Para消,,0,0,0,,Ah! Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:10.65,Para消,,0,0,0,,You want me to sneak into the staff room and reclaim your nintendo switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:11.80,Para光,,0,0,0,,Hey, that loud voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.73,Para光,,0,0,0,,You're "able to leave no trace", so I'm asking this favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:15.67,Para光,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to be so loud
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:17.69,Para消,,0,0,0,,Ah, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:20.48,Para消,,0,0,0,,But well, you having something confiscated is unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:25.12,Para光,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, I was playing in secret during class, and he noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:26.92,Para光,,0,0,0,,Well, there is something embarassing..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:29.73,Para光,,0,0,0,,While playing the game, I got a rare item...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:32.44,Para光,,0,0,0,,Without thinking, I lit up, which is more embarassing than gaming on the sly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:36.20,Para光,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:44.17,Para光,,0,0,0,,Did he already go? Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:45.88,Para消,,0,0,0,,No, I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:47.75,Para消,,0,0,0,,I'm still right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:48.98,Para光,,0,0,0,,Ah, you were still there
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:50.67,Para光,,0,0,0,,Stop suddenly erasing your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:52.67,Para光,,0,0,0,,Since I really can't tell when you've erased your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:53.75,Para消,,0,0,0,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:55.27,Para光,,0,0,0,,Anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:57.86,Para光,,0,0,0,,If you get back my switch, I'll treat you to whatever you want
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:00.08,Para消,,0,0,0,,huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:00.91,Para消,,0,0,0,,Heck yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:03.98,Para光,,0,0,0,,No, that's loud, too loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:06.10,Para光,,0,0,0,,You really have a real loud voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:08.24,Para光,,0,0,0,,Anyway, think about what food you want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:10.24,Para光,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:13.19,Para光,,0,0,0,,Well... it's about time huh..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:14.65,Para光,,0,0,0,,Well, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:17.20,Para光,,0,0,0,,... huh? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:22.79,Para光,,0,0,0,,Did he go... I wonder ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:23.99,Para光,,0,0,0,,This time it definitely feels like he went... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:24.59,Para消,,0,0,0,,Mac!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:25.04,Para光,,0,0,0,,Uwah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:26.65,Para消,,0,0,0,,Mac! Samurai Mac is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:29.98,Para消,,0,0,0,,The broiled soy sauce double-patty one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:33.17,Para光,,0,0,0,,You startled me.... you were still there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:35.82,Para光,,0,0,0,,Just now I totally thought you'd already gone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:39.03,Para消,,0,0,0,,No, I wouldn't leave in the middle of a conversation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:42.26,Para消,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about what I wanted to be treated to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:45.04,Para光,,0,0,0,,I mean, could you not "presence erase" and then suddenly yell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:47.35,Para光,,0,0,0,,It really startled me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:48.40,Para消,,0,0,0,,My bad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:51.14,Para光,,0,0,0,,That other time, on the train, you erased your presence..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:55.22,Para光,,0,0,0,,When you gave your seat to that old person they were super startled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:59.82,Para消,,0,0,0,,Aah, the old lady looked like she was about to faint
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:02.95,Para光,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because your loud voice startled her huh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:06.44,Para光,,0,0,0,,When you offered your seat your presence was erased so wouldn't quietly leaving the seat be better
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:08.36,Para消,,0,0,0,,Ah, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:11.32,Para消,,0,0,0,,You're smart! Ahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:13.32,Para光,,0,0,0,,Like I said, your voice is loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:17.21,Para光,,0,0,0,,Anyway, about now there shouldn't be many teachers in the teacher's lounge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.98,Para光,,0,0,0,,...hey, you're still there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:26.36,Para光,,0,0,0,,... hey, say something already
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:31.23,Para光,,0,0,0,,This time, it's like he really went
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.46,Para光,,0,0,0,,That guy, wasn't he just saying nonsense like "I wouldn't leave in the middle of a conversation"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.27,Para消,,0,0,0,,Hey, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:39.44,Para消,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:41.70,Para消,,0,0,0,,Please return Hikaru's Switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:44.90,Para光,,0,0,0,,Huh, really...? The significance of presence concealment....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:47.71,Para消,,0,0,0,,Yes! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.67,Para消,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.95,Para消,,0,0,0,,Switch delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:54.84,Para消,,0,0,0,,Just apologizing was good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:58.96,Para消,,0,0,0,,Right, and now samurai mac!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:03.19,Para光,,0,0,0,,Well, it was a waste of the ability, but it fits you
